{"about_the_game":"Orestorm Factory is inspired by automation games, but with an action twist.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery resource your factory produces is dangerous to the player, forcing you to balance moment-to-moment dodging with long term strategy and base building.<br />\r\nIssues compound as exponentially more enemies spawn the longer you're alive. Live long enough, and you'll awaken the monster that lurks in the cavern.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you die, the resources you harvested can be used to power up your character for future runs. Making every get a little bit easier until you find that sweet spot and finally beat the game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt also contains a roguelike mode where you must beat it in a single run, making you really test your mettle.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1674603876","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183740/page.bg.jpg?t=1674603876","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183740/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1674603876","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183740/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1674603876","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2219920,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Orestorm Factory is inspired by automation games, but with an action twist.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery resource your factory produces is dangerous to the player, forcing you to balance moment-to-moment dodging with long term strategy and base building.<br />\r\nIssues compound as exponentially more enemies spawn the longer you're alive. Live long enough, and you'll awaken the monster that lurks in the cavern.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you die, the resources you harvested c